        {
            "title": "民調：近半數英國民眾認為新預算不公平 三分之二料未來一年經濟惡化",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 根據<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:預算案;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/預算案\">預算案</a>公佈後的首次民調結果，英國民眾對財政大臣蕾切爾·里夫斯的預算案反應相當負面，表明工黨政府低迷的支持率恐難見起色。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在周三預算案公佈後進行的YouGov民調中，48%的受訪者認為預算案不公平，僅21%認為公平。這是YouGov自2010年開始追蹤預算案民意以來的第二差評分，僅好於2022年保守黨前首相特拉斯推出的那份引發市場動盪的「迷你預算案」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dYcc7yEt6qsC_BcRa4MwfQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2c016e7b6f0d67da836084e3f76df86f\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">半數受訪者認為里夫斯的預算案將使他們和家庭的經濟狀況惡化，僅3%認為會改善。只有3%的受訪者認為經濟處於「相當好的」狀態，認為「非常好」者為0%。三分之二受訪者預期未來12個月經濟將惡化。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-09abd008-6dc6-34e4-b329-16ba3c9e79c8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">YouGov調查發現部分具體措施頗受歡迎，例如降低能源費、凍結鐵路票價，以及對豪宅和博彩徵收新稅。但多數受訪者認為，此時提高工薪階層稅收和擴大家庭福利實屬不當之舉。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Almost Half of Britons View Budget as Unfair, Poll Shows (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 James Woolcock、Ellen Milligan.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E6%95%B8%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E6%96%B0%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3-%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%8C%E6%96%99%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%83%A1%E5%8C%96-100856701.html",
